cident I used to get straight A's. Now I have a B minus. I'm pretty amazed I made the spelling bee even though I won a lot of them before. `` I just want to be treated like a regular <PERSON> Joe </PERSON> <PERSON> Schmo </PERSON>, really,'' he added. `` Some of my friends tease me and tell me I have brain damage, but they stick up for me.''
