<HEAD>Fund-Raiser Wright Helped Is Indicted In Iowa Finance Scheme</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By PETE YOST</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
