at they are seeking some kind of <ORGANIZATION> FDIC </ORGANIZATION> assistance should create some additional confidence in the system.'' <PERSON> Anderson </PERSON> said that if it takes an infusion of federal money to get the bank on its feet, `` that's the way it's going to have to be.'
